      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age. The engine and transmission are fully operational, but you should expect minor fluid seepage and a bit of a rougher ride than a newer model. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor paint fading, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and some cracked plastic trim. It is a solid, functional car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics and is willing to keep up with routine maintenance.",
